478
00:28:44,760 --> 00:28:47,159
Tapi aku yang memukulnya pingsan.

479
00:28:47,160 --> 00:28:50,310
Baiklah, mari kita kembali dulu.

480
00:28:50,310 --> 00:28:52,919
Tuanku, mengenai kakakku yang melepaskan Xu Rugui...

481
00:28:52,919 --> 00:28:55,500
Dia sudah menebus kesalahannya. Dia sudah dibebaskan.

482
00:28:55,500 --> 00:28:56,580
Terima kasih, Tuanku.

483
00:28:56,580 --> 00:28:59,180
Bawa Xu Rugui pergi.

484
00:28:59,180 --> 00:29:01,780
